description:
Recently sold: $184,500. Coveted Ely Lake Area - Fayal Township, near two beaches, boat landings, bike trail and groomed snowmobile trail.  This home is a turn-key totally remodeled home on a 2 acre corner lot with mature pines & hardwoods.  The home has city sewer and natural gas heating.
Updates:
1995 - new drilled well, home was reinsulated, vinyl sided and maintenance free windows were installed.
2008 - completely remodeled home with new wiring, plumbing, tongue & groove 3/4" knotty pine throughout, new sheet rock walls in kitchen & bathroom, repaired textured & painted all ceilings, new interior & exterior doors, new vinyl & carpeted flooring throughout, new lighting throughout, new bathroom tub/shower enclosure along with toilet/sink/vanity, new kitchen cabinets & appliances, new outside decks.
2015 - installed new Carrier furnace & central air conditioner.  Reroofed home & basement was waterproofed.
2016 - new vinyl siding was done to home & both garages.
2018 - new Hague water conditioning system was installed.
2019 - new stairway built into the basement along with newly painted basement walls & floor.

Garage #1 - 25'x25' totally remodeled in 2008 - new concrete floor, new wiring, insulation, sheeting, lighting and Hot Dog heater.  New roof in 2012 and new siding in 2016.

Garage #2 - 28'x32' built in 2010, wired and has concrete floor, new vinyl siding in 2016.
